<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. ـهِ وَلاَ مُسَاوَاةٍ وَلاَ نُقْصَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مَا خَلْقُ آدَمَ بِاليَدِيْنِ بِمُوْجِبٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَضْلاً عَلَى المَبْعُوْثِ بِالقُرْآنِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَكَذَا خَصَائِصُ مَنْ أَتَى مِنْ بَعْدِهِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مِنْ كُلِّ رُسْلِ اللهِ بِالبُرْهَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَمُحَمَّدٌ أَعْلاَهُمُ فَوْقاً وَمَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>حَكمتَ لَهُمْ بِمَزِيَّةِ الرُّجْحَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَالحَائِزُ الخَمْسِيْنَ أَجْراً لم يَحُزْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>هَا فِي جَمِْيعِ شَرَائِعِ الإيمان<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>هَلْ حَازَهَا إِذْ كَانَ قَدْ عَدِمَ المُعِيْـ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>نَ وَهُمْ فَقَدْ كَانُوْا أْولِي أَعْوَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>والرَّبُ لَيْسَ يُضِيْعُ مَا يَتَحَمَّلُ الْـ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مُتَحَمَّلُونَ لأَجْلِهِ مِنْ شَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَتَحَمُّلِ الْعَبْد الوَحْيِدِ رِضَاهُ مَعْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَيْضِ الْعَدُوِّ وَقِلَّةِ الأعْوَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مِمَّا يَدُلَّ عَلَى يَقِيْنٍ صَادِقٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَمَحَبَّةٍ وحَقِيْقَةِ العِرْفَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>يَكْفِيه ذُلاً وَاغْتِرَاباً قِلَّةُ الْـ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَنْصَارِ بَيْنَ عَسَاكِرِ الشَّيْطَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فِي كُلّ يَوْمٍ فِرْقَةٌ تَغْزُوْهُ إِنْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>تَرْجِعْ يُوَافِيه الفَرِيْقُ الثَّانِي<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>